      <title>游戏与游戏化</title>
      <link>https://blog.uglyboy.cn/slides/2018/01/29/%E6%B8%B8%E6%88%8F%E4%B8%8E%E6%B8%B8%E6%88%8F%E5%8C%96/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Jan 2018 10:24:35 +0800</pubDate>
      <guid>https://blog.uglyboy.cn/slides/2018/01/29/%E6%B8%B8%E6%88%8F%E4%B8%8E%E6%B8%B8%E6%88%8F%E5%8C%96/</guid>
      <description>&lt;div class=&#34;reveal&#34;&gt;
